> <br />\n好sad"},{"pid":"2a1c96c1b4eaa6d9eba3815ab1b3e6bf0b103dd8","tid":479632,"uid":2436,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T17:14:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8dd475925362c5b19b5763a35bacfb62239a1176","tid":479632,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T17:19:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"abfc2fa86221f750e29c2db3dabab6311ece44a2","tid":479632,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T17:20:58.000Z","msg":"學校設新校規打壓又真係吹佢唔漲"},{"pid":"eb341a85c97b421d047d5a1c459fe76539147453","tid":479632,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:08:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>離開左中學呢個溫室你咩都唔係呀小朋友<br />\n係學校勇抗極權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 笑撚死人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1bc9bf7a720e56e2252c3a92ff775e2d343b80","tid":479632,"uid":71725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T01:11:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}